# Protected Areas Approval

Before editing anything that can affect any protected area, stop and tell the user exactly which protected area will be affected, then wait for explicit approval.

Protected areas:
- `/cruises` page, cruises components, cruises scroll reveal, `PageScrollTransition`, `usePageScrollTransition`, and shared transition CSS that can affect cruises.
- Booking system and booking pages, including `/booking/**`, booking APIs, checkout, availability, holds, confirmations, and booking UI components.
- Admin dashboard, including `/admin/**`, `/api/admin/**`, dashboard upload/save flows, dashboard UI components, and dashboard auth.

This applies even if the protected change seems necessary for the prompt. Do not make the edit first.
